OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1782294489
OL,3,CTrial of man accused of two murders to
OL,4,Cbegin after remains found in woods
OL,6,FA jury has been sworn in for the trial
OL,7,Fof a man from Cornwall accused of
OL,8,Fmurdering two other men.
OL,10,FJames Desborough, 40, is accused of
OL,11,Fmurdering Claudio Aquilino, 57,
OL,12,Fsometime between 17 April and 7 July
OL,13,F2025 and Daniel Coleman, 43, between 2
OL,14,FJune and 7 July 2025.
OL,16,FA large police search took place in
OL,17,FSticker near St Austell at the time,
OL,18,Fwith specialist forensic officers at
OL,19,Fthe scene for several days.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
