PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1782294489
OL,3,CTrial of man accused of two murders to
OL,4,Cbegin after remains found in woods
OL,6,FOn Monday 22 June, a jury of eight men
OL,7,Fand four women was sworn in to try the
OL,8,Fcase at Winchester Crown Court.
OL,10,FMr Justice Saini told the jury that
OL,11,Fthe trial would be opened by the
OL,12,Fprosecution on Wednesday and was
OL,13,Fexpected to last up to seven weeks.
OL,15,F"You will have heard the defendant
OL,16,Ffaces the most serious charge any
OL,17,Fperson can face in the English courts
OL,18,F` that of murder," the judge told the
OL,19,Fjury.
OL,26,@wD@AOUzD@RO]
