CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1782294489
OL,3,CTrial of man accused of two murders to
OL,4,Cbegin after remains found in woods
OL,6,F"On Wednesday, I am going to give you
OL,7,Fmore legal instructions but what's
OL,8,Fgoing to happen is, I am going to send
OL,9,Fyou away because the court is dealing
OL,10,Fwith other matters.
OL,12,F"You should not do any research online
OL,13,Fabout this case. There may well be
OL,14,Fnews stories about this case online or
OL,15,Fin newspapers.
OL,17,F"Ordinary internet use is fine but do
OL,18,Fnot go looking for news about this
OL,19,Fcase. You should not do your own
OL,20,Fresearch.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
