PN,40704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1782294489
OL,3,CTrial of man accused of two murders to
OL,4,Cbegin after remains found in woods
OL,6,F"When you return, I will give you more
OL,7,Flegal directions and you will hear
OL,8,Ffrom the prosecution about what this
OL,9,Fcase is about."
OL,11,FAhmed Hossain KC and Leila Tai are
OL,12,Fappearing for the prosecution.
OL,14,FDesborough, of Old Oak Woods, Lower
OL,15,FSticker, Cornwall, is represented by
OL,16,FSean Brunton KC and Paul Grumbar.
OL,18,FThe trial was adjourned.
